===Etymology 1===
{{wp|ja:[[魂 (曖昧さ回避)|魂]]}}
{{ja-kanjitab|たましい|yomi=k|alt=魄|clearright=y}}
{{IPAfont|⟨tamasipi<sub>1</sub>⟩}} → *{{IPAchar|/tamasipʲi/}} → {{IPAchar|/tamaɕifi/}} → {{IPAchar|/tamaɕiwi/}} → {{IPAchar|/tamaɕiː/}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|-}}.

Compound of {{m|ja||魂|tr=tama|[[soul]], [[spirit]]|pos=see below}} and an uncertain ''shii'', possibly {{m|ja||強ひ|tr=shihi → shii}}, the {{m|ja|連用形|tr=ren'yōkei||stem or continuative form}} of classical verb {{m|ja|強ふ|tr= shifu → shiu}}, modern {{m|ja|強いる|tr=shiiru||to [[force]], [[compel]]}}. {{rfv-etym|ja}}

